Quaker Oats' 100% Natural Claim Questioned In Lawsuit
The New York Times,
Tuesday, May 3, 2016 8 AM
Recommend (1)
A lawsuit seeking to be certified as aclassactionhas been filed on behalf of consumers in New York and California against
the owner of Quaker Oats after testing found traces of the pesticide glyphosate in some oatmeal.
2SHARES
Read the whole story at The New York Times
